{"tid":1407021,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"唔知大家記唔記得學生時代嘅一樣嘢","createTime":"2019-08-04T14:38:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T14:42:35.000Z","uid":212050,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"cc1164c7332989492e6a248f23464450ea241c23","tid":1407021,"uid":212050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T14:38:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">記得以前中小學嘅廁所一般係唔會有紙巾俾你用，要你自備或者係問人借。<br />\n除左因為學校窮之外，仲有一樣要防嘅就係防啲人<span style=\"color: red;\">將紙巾濕水再掟上埲天花板度</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">啲濕水紙巾會黐住係度滴水，乾左仲會留左一舊紙係埲牆度</span></span>好鬼核突<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">所以大家如果要掟嘢</span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">千祈唔好學</span>，<span style=\"font-size: large;\">如果唔係留左一嚿嚿紙團係人地幅牆度就好難搞。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"75e95311f824b9743d7c096becceaa65ac2daf37","tid":1407021,"uid":212050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T14:39:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e056f4b5c06649a7a05ea8af0823b1bd0c7e3946","tid":1407021,"uid":212050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T14:40:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"55c10d5806d355b740eba96b473fb88abd04242b","tid":1407021,"uid":237614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T14:42:35.000Z","msg":"以前掟響吊扇度<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}